
Use a vanilla environment (do not source Geant4 dependencies)

```
make
[plot]$ ./steps --help
Usage: ./sim <options>
Options:
        -i,--input              Input ROOT file
        -o,--output             Output image
        -m,--model              Model ascii file
        -d,--density            Density [g/cm3]
```

Examples:
   ./steps -i ../build/output1MeV_Livermore.root -o plot1MeV_Livermore.png -m ../scripts/estar_STP; eog plot1MeV_Livermore.png
   ./steps -i ../build/he4_10MeV_Livermore.root -d 0.1 -o plothe4_10MeV_Livermore.png -m ../scripts/estar_He3; eog plothe4_10MeV_Livermore.png
